{"tid":1133633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞平時喺西甲牙刷刷，今晚對利記將會見識到乜嘢係絕望。","createTime":"2019-05-01T08:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T23:38:35.000Z","uid":44285,"like":26,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"70449e76d29a9b3d1311ddaf8e5113e9b3382b22","tid":1133633,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"巴塞平時喺西甲牙刷刷，今晚對利記將會見識到乜嘢係絕望。<br />\n可能唔踢第二場都已經知道自己要專心踢國王盃了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利記今年狀態良好， 積分榜破紀錄。<br />\n巴塞主要射手都只係阿根廷沙拿， 今次同真正沙拿同場較技，<br />\n 唔使諗都知係正版贏，老翻實輸到七個一皮。<br />\n<br />\n再加上有英甲仔羅拔臣， 一定大爆巴塞隆拿右路防守， 攻擊疤狗防守弱點。<br />\n<br />\n今晚利物浦雖然作客，但正如傳奇領隊高普話齋：Camp Nou is not a temple. 利記一定勝券在握， 有多餘閑錢嘅朋友可以考慮按左層樓。聽朝可以準備買定第二層。<br />\n<br />\n風水佬可能呃你十年八年， 我醉右一晚就可以幫你發達。"},{"pid":"24c4699b6dfd56eb766358f359f612bbeec28028","tid":1133633,"uid":13492,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"留名bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5bf071b53ec6f7fe74addaa0eb8eaadbb30225","tid":1133633,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24c4699b6dfd56eb766358f359f612bbeec28028","tid":1133633,"uid":13492,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"留名bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"巴塞呢啲山寨王做返西超霸主算數啦<br />\n<br />\n連續三年做八弟"},{"pid":"7bd220cdbff8e1dda2d1222d40ae5d92cc42347a","tid":1133633,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7422a3927be2db24f04f19126d7c76febb19acb3","tid":1133633,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bd220cdbff8e1dda2d1222d40ae5d92cc42347a","tid":1133633,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"碎<